attributes.text:
The TR-064 plugin and widget creates a interface to routers that are configured by the TR-064 protocol, like the well known Fritz!Box routers.

The protocol is described at: https://avm.de/service/schnittstellen/

0.11.0

Christian Mayer
Parses the widgets XML configuration and extracts the given information to a simple key/value map.
extracted data from config element as key/value map
